data.description: Vibrant luminosity abounds in this Lairds residence. Wrapped in a classic brick exterior, a covered front porch welcomes residents into an easily flowing layout cascading w/ wood flooring and large windows throughout. A bright and spacious living area offers plenty of room for both relaxing and entertaining. Sliding glass doors open to a covered patio in an expansive backyard featuring privacy fencing, a firepit area and a raised garden bed. Peer over a breakfast bar w/ seating into an upgraded kitchen showcasing stainless steel appliances, generous cabinetry and contemporary light fixtures. Two sizable bedrooms share an updated bath w/ neutral tiles. Downstairs, a finished lower level offers flexible living space w/ a living area, kitchenette, bedroom and an updated bath. Residents may use this space as private guest accommodation or for rental income potential. Ideally located to both downtown and the mountains, residents enjoy easy access to parks, outdoor recreation and shopping.
